---
title: Smart Pesto Chicken Salad with Baby Spinach and Toasted Almonds
description: Juicy roasted chicken sits on a generous pile of baby spinach and toasted almonds. Crispy cucumbers and juicy tomatoes bring the best of summer's produce to every bite!
